    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rods with a flanged or shaped end inserted into chocolate pots through an aperture in the lid or cover and twirled so as to stir and froth the beverage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
